title: Beowulf (Speakeasy Comics)
description:
Once called Beowulf, now the great warrior lives in Manhattan and goes by the simpler name of Wulf. He alone knows that a coming world-threat has triggered a sudden power influx creating super-powered beings around the world, but even Wulf is in the dark as to what horrific shape that threat will take.

Written by Brian Augustyn and illustrated by Dub.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
